"1. 确认扩展已在 Safari 设置 > 扩展 中启用。\n2. 检查全局开关是否为「始终开启」或「跟随系统」（系统需为深色模式）。\n3. 尝试刷新当前网页。\n4. 重启 Safari 后再试。" = "1. Make sure the extension is enabled in Safari Settings > Extensions.\n2. Check whether the global switch is set to \"Always On\" or \"Follow System\" (system must be in dark mode).\n3. Try refreshing the current page.\n4. Restart Safari and try again.";
"DarkReader 不收集、不上传任何用户数据。所有网页解析、颜色计算均在您的设备本地完成，不会发送到任何服务器。" = "NightGuard does not collect or upload any user data. All webpage parsing and color computation happen locally on your device.";
